metadata.name: Tiamond #001
metadata.description: This Tiamond NFT represents ownership of a natural diamond, GIA graded, stored in a secure vault. The token can be traded without friction, while the diamond remains stored in special security vaults at the highest security levels. Tiamonds #001 is a 0.3 Carat, round shape diamond with a Very Good Cut, J Color, and VVS1 Clarity.
